code class=\"bg(gray-50) c(purple-700) px(xs) py(0.5) r(sm) border(1/gray-200) font(mono) text(sm)\">animate(pulse)\u003C/code>\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3>Position &amp; Display\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cul class=\"list(disc) pl(xl) my(lg)\">\u003Cli>\u003Ccode class=\"bg(gray-50) c(purple-700) px(xs) py(0.5) r(sm) border(1/gray-200) font(mono) text(sm)\">relative\u003C/code>, \u003Ccode class=\"bg(gray-50) c(purple-700) px(xs) py(0.5) r(sm) border(1/gray-200) font(mono) text(sm)\">absolute\u003C/code>, \u003Ccode class=\"bg(gray-50) c(purple-700) px(xs) py(0.5) r(sm) border(1/gray-200) font(mono) text(sm)\">fixed\u003C/code> → \u003Ccode class=\"bg(gray-50) c(purple-700) px(xs) py(0.5) r(sm) border(1/gray-200) font(mono) text(sm)\">relative\u003C/code>, \u003Ccode class=\"bg(gray-50) c(purple-700) px(xs) py(0.5) r(sm) border(1/gray-200) font(mono) text(sm)\">absolute\u003C/code>, \u003Ccode class=\"bg(gray-50) c(purple-700) px(xs) py(0.5) r(sm) border(1/gray-200) font(mono) text(sm)\">fixed\u003C/code> (keep as-is)\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Ccode class=\"bg(gray-50) c(purple-700) px(xs) py(0.5) r(sm) border(1/gray-200) font(mono) text(sm)\">inset-0\u003C/code> → \u003Ccode class=\"bg(gray-50) c(purple-700) px(xs) py(0.5) r(sm) border(1/gray-200) font(mono) text(sm)\">inset(0)\u003C/code>\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Ccode class=\"bg(gray-50) c(purple-700) px(xs) py(0.5) r(sm) border(1/gray-200) font(mono) text(sm)\">min-h-screen\u003C/code> → \u003Ccode class=\"bg(gray-50) c(purple-700) px(xs) py(0.5) r(sm) border(1/gray-200) font(mono) text(sm)\">min-h(screen)\u003C/code>\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Ccode class=\"bg(gray-50) c(purple-700) px(xs) py(0.5) r(sm) border(1/gray-200) font(mono) text(sm)\">max-w-2xl\u003C/code> → \u003Ccode class=\"bg(gray-50) c(purple-700) px(xs) py(0.5) r(sm) border(1/gray-200) font(mono) text(sm)\">max-w(2xl)\u003C/code>\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Ccode class=\"bg(gray-50) c(purple-700) px(xs) py(0.5) r(sm) border(1/gray-200) font(mono) text(sm)\">